6.人都是利益共同体

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appEOYSm4kc8307/a_5ca1d9ce6b86c_26Fiumao

<section><section><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/87629500_1553655379.jpg" alt="" style="border: 0px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;"/></p><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: rgb(204, 204, 204) 3px 3px 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding: 0px 30px; text-align: right; height: 60px; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/4083900_1553655380.com/mmbiz_png/fgnkxfgnnkqijuunxqkg3icyslyianzheyrq3xxgchqsazvgy21kvy0orc742prf5vlqpfu13ujxheuaiaft43wxg/0?wx_fmt=png&#39;); background-repeat: repeat-x; background-size: auto 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; padding-top: 15px; width: 30px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/60697300_1553655380.com/mmbiz_png/fgnkxfgnnkqijuunxqkg3icyslyianzheyo0tmukdknziamtpxos1dr5alqbqmrqr2dwfwnmkcsd1typixyoajktg/0"/></section></section><section style="width:100%; display:flex; display:-webkit-flex; margin-top:-30px;"><section style="border-bottom: 30px solid rgb(245, 244, 240); border-left: 30px solid transparent; margin-left: 30px; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="height: 30px; background-color: rgb(245, 244, 240); line-height: 30px; padding: 0px 10px; color: rgb(65, 66, 66); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>左宗棠说：</strong></span></section></section><section style="padding: 20px; background-color: rgb(245, 244, 240); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(65, 66, 66); box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>“阳明先生，其事功，其志业，卓然一代伟人，断非寻常儒者所能几及。</strong></span>”</span></section></section></section></section><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f3f;">王阳明被廷杖，被贬谪 ，被陷害，被追杀，每次他都从容应对，云淡风轻，其临终遗言“此心光明，亦复何言“更是成为千古绝唱。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f3f;">无论何时何地，都没有人能替我们看顾我们的内心，此心之友光明了，世界才会光明。</span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f3f;">王阳明“白死千难“的一生，就是一场灵魂的徒步。 我们了解王阳明，学习阳明心学，让灵魂安定下来，让心不再为外物所动，智慧自然而来。</span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;"><br/></p><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%;"><section style="width: 100%;border-left: dashed 2px #534a47;background:#f5f5f5;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(63, 62, 63); padding: 0.5em; box-sizing: border-box;"><p><strong><span style="font-size: 15px;">阳明心学是2500年来中国文化的又一座高峰，是中国人结合儒释道之精妙之处的神奇智慧。</span></strong></p></section></section><section style="display: flex;justify-content: flex-end;margin-top: -20px;"><section style="width: 0px; height: 0px; border-bottom: 20px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); border-left: 20px solid transparent; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f3f;">王阳明在继承前人智慧的基础上创立了独具光芒的阳明心学，参透世事人心，终成一代圣哲，对其后500年的中国历史产生了不可替代的影响。</span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="white-space: normal; padding-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-left: 5px solid rgb(157, 180, 194); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 13px;text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(102, 102, 102,0.8);"><p style="margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">曾国藩研习阳明心学，编练湘军进攻太平天国，历时十二年克尽全功；</span></p><p style="margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">稻盛</span><span style="font-size: 15px;">和夫将阳明心学应用于现代企业管理，缔造了两家“世界500强”企业，成为日本“经营之圣”。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">蒋介石与毛泽东对中国发展的道路选择大相径庭，但对阳明心学却一样的推崇和拜服；</span></p></section><p style="font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #666666; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: #7f7f7f;">习近平主席也提到阳明心学。</span></p></section></section><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center;"><img src="https://ss3.bdstatic.com/70cFv8Sh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=3568768376,983816345&fm=26&gp=0.jpg" class="loadingclass"/><br/></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f3f;">做管理也是一场灵魂的修炼，伟大的企业家也都是哲学家，都行走在磨练、修行的路上。</span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f3f;">如何致良知，知行合一的精髓到底是什么，如何做到知行合一，如何做到心外无物，心即理的内涵是什么，如何世上磨，如何把阳明心学的精髓与企业管理真正结合起来并落实到日常工作中去……</span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f3f;">对这些问题的回答与解决，就是企业家和决策层的修行，是灵魂的徒步，是管理智慧的再现。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: #3f3f3f;">阳明心学是直指人心、又能引导企业家赢在起跑线上的学问。因为使用者的这种感觉是你带给他的，他就会与你风雨兼程，构成了你企业的价值链的一环，不会见“利”思迁，这就是德鲁克说的：<strong><span style="color: rgb(227, 108, 9);">“创造顾客！”</span></strong></span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/3109300_1553655381.jpg" alt="" style="border: 0px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: block;"/></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f3f;">李安老师传播阳明心学大有“替往圣继绝学，为万世开太平”的情怀，这源自于他读大学的时候就深感为什么本民族的原创力在世界民族之林中落后。</span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f3f;">当时他就发现，管理学理论全是来自西方的，哲学理论、管理哲学也是围绕西方价值观转，使他常常扼腕叹息。</span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px; color: #3f3f3f;">当他找到阳明心学，发现心学中蕴藏的巨大现代性启蒙潜能和庞大哲学体系的构建可能时，就再也对心学难舍难弃，开发出阳明心学与企业管理系列课程。</span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: #e36c09;"><strong><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 15px;">财富是思想的外现，思想是财富的源泉，阳明心学就是实现财富外现、打通思想心源的学问，企业家们必备。</span></strong></span></p><p style="border: 0px; margin: 0.63em 10px 10px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: #191919; font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/41456500_1553655381.jpg" alt="微信图片_20170828150958.jpg"/></p><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;text-align: center;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: #000000 0px 0px 0px 0px; line-height: 2; padding: 10px; background-color: #e8e6df; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 10px; border-style: none; border-color: #3e3e3e; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box; color: #746d54;"><section style="margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border-width: 2px; border-style: dotted; border-color: #e8e6df; padding: 10px; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 30%;box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/63493600_1553655381.com/cache/remote/ahr0chm6ly9tbwjpei5xbg9nby5jbi9tbwjpel9qcgcvbgrgyujou2t2sglhzk9kchowaly4mm9wn2pgdfrzowvisgzxtdr6euy4bmfpy0lpy1bnzvdrohjcvnzlclvyu1nxqmlimfhbr0xzawnqvddorfezm2